{"header":"<h1>Module <code><span>Svalue.Make</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"soteria","href":"../../../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Soteria","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Bv_values","href":"../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Svalue","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Make","href":"#","kind":"module"}],"toc":[{"title":"Parameters","href":"#parameters","children":[]},{"title":"Signature","href":"#signature","children":[{"title":"Operator declarations","href":"#operator-declarations","children":[]},{"title":"Booleans","href":"#booleans","children":[]},{"title":"Pointers","href":"#pointers","children":[]},{"title":"Sequences","href":"#sequences","children":[]},{"title":"General constructors","href":"#general-constructors","children":[]},{"title":"Infix operators","href":"#infix-operators","children":[]}]}],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"<p>Builds the untyped svalue layer for extension <code>V</code>: the value/type definitions specialised to <code>V</code>, the hash-cons table, and the simplifying smart constructors (<a href=\"module-type-Bool/index.html\" title=\"Make.Bool\"><code>Bool</code></a>, <a href=\"module-type-BitVec/index.html\" title=\"Make.BitVec\"><code>BitVec</code></a>, <a href=\"module-type-Float/index.html\" title=\"Make.Float\"><code>Float</code></a>, <a href=\"Ptr/index.html\" title=\"Make.Ptr\"><code>Ptr</code></a>, <a href=\"SSeq/index.html\" title=\"Make.SSeq\"><code>SSeq</code></a>, ...). This is the foundation the rest of <code>Bv_values</code> is built on; most callers reach it as <code>Typed.Svalue</code> rather than applying it directly (see <a href=\"../../Typed/Make/index.html\"><code>Typed.Make</code></a>).</p><p><code>Make</code> is <b>generative</b> (note the final <code>()</code>): each application mints a fresh, abstract <code>ghost</code> tagging every value it hash-conses, and owns its own table. Two applications — even to the same <code>V</code> — therefore produce mutually incompatible <code>t</code>s, so values from one can never be mixed with another's. Apply it once and share the resulting module.</p>","content":"<h2 id=\"parameters\"><a href=\"#parameters\" class=\"anchor\"></a>Parameters</h2><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec parameter anchored\" id=\"argument-1-V\"><a href=\"#argument-1-V\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> </span><span><a href=\"argument-1-V/index.html\">V</a></span><span> : <a href=\"../module-type-Value_ext/index.html\">Value_ext</a></span></code></div></div><h2 id=\"signature\"><a href=\"#signature\" class=\"anchor\"></a>Signature</h2><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Ext\"><a href=\"#module-Ext\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> Ext</span><span> = <a href=\"argument-1-V/index.html\">V</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Unop\"><a href=\"#module-Unop\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> Unop</span><span> = <a href=\"../Unop/index.html\">Unop</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Binop\"><a href=\"#module-Binop\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> Binop</span><span> = <a href=\"../Binop/index.html\">Binop</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Nop\"><a href=\"#module-Nop\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> Nop</span><span> = <a href=\"../Nop/index.html\">Nop</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-RoundingMode\"><a href=\"#module-RoundingMode\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> RoundingMode</span><span> = <a href=\"../RoundingMode/index.html\">RoundingMode</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-FloatClass\"><a href=\"#module-FloatClass\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> FloatClass</span><span> = <a href=\"../FloatClass/index.html\">FloatClass</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-FloatPrecision\"><a href=\"#module-FloatPrecision\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> FloatPrecision</span><span> = <a href=\"../FloatPrecision/index.html\">FloatPrecision</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Var\"><a href=\"#module-Var\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> Var</span><span> = <a href=\"../../../Symex/Var/index.html\">Var</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type anchored\" id=\"type-ghost\"><a href=\"#type-ghost\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> ghost</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>The fresh, abstract ghost identifying this application of <a href=\"#\"><code>Make</code></a>.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-equal_ghost\"><a href=\"#val-equal_ghost\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> equal_ghost : <span><span class=\"type-var\">'a</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span class=\"type-var\">'b</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> bool</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type anchored\" id=\"type-ty\"><a href=\"#type-ty\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"keyword\">nonrec</span> ty</span><span> = <span><span><a href=\"#type-ghost\">ghost</a> <a href=\"argument